    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他语声一顿，目光利剪似地在那胖灵官面上一瞪，又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我展白年轻识浅，对这一套全不懂，我只知道这趟镖是茹老镖头交给我的，我就该把它送到地头，各位朋友要是看得起我展白，就请让个道，我展白来日必有补报之处，否则——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "否则怎的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "力劈华山",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "凤凰展翅",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三才剑",
      "tone": "陈述",
